# ============================================
# Secrets
# ============================================
# S1a adds none. The decision-record hash is unkeyed by design: a hash detects accidental
# mutation and costs nothing, while a signature would defend against forgery by someone who
# already holds the Vault credentials and could spend directly. See C-001 section 9.
#
# S1b (execution governance) and S8/S9 (Google Ads connector) add credentials here.
